{"name": "odoo14-addon-vault-share", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-vault-share", "version": "14.0.1.2.1", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/server-auth", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-vault", "odoo"], "summary": "Implementation of a mechanism to share secrets", "upload_time": 1673605165}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fserver--auth-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/server-auth\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/server-auth/tree/14.0/vault_share\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/server-auth-14-0/server-auth-14-0-vault_share\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/251/14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Vault - Share\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module implements possibilities to share specific secrets with external users. This bases on the vault implementation and the generated RSA key pair.\n\n## Share\n\nThis allows an user to share a secret with external users. A share can be generated from a vault entry or directly created by an user. The secret is symmetrically encrypted by a key derived from a pin. To grant access the user has to transmit the link and pin with the external. If either the access counter reaches 0 or the share expires it will be deleted automatically. Due to the usage of a numeric pin and the browser side decryption a share is vulnerable to brute-force attacks and shouldn't be used as a permanent storage for secrets. For long time uses the user should create an account and a vault should be used.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/server-auth/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/server-auth/issues/new?body=module:%20vault_share%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- initOS GmbH\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Florian Kantelberg \\<<mailto:florian.kantelberg@initos.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/server-auth](https://github.com/OCA/server-auth/tree/14.0/vault_share) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log", "documentation": ["\u00a9 2021 Florian Kantelberg - initOS GmbH", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log._logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log.VaultShareLog", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log.VaultShareLog._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log.VaultShareLog._description", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log.VaultShareLog._order", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log.VaultShareLog.share_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log.VaultShareLog.name", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models", "documentation": ["\u00a9 2021 Florian Kantelberg - initOS GmbH", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models..res_config_settings", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models..vault_share", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models.vault_share_log", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.vault_share.models..vault_share_log", "project": 